column5: The wife showed me that video a couple weeks ago. Great video. Man I love it when he says 3 and the dog gets his ball. I also love when the owner says "don't look at it"! lol
"Sneak Peak"  awesome!  I wonder if he can train my kids to be that obedient and patient?
I saw it earlier this week. I wish my pooch were half as smart as this one.

Well, I decided to make an attempt and confirming that indeed, this is the world's smartest dog. I showed the video to my dog, "Lucky".  After close scrutiny, he suggested that this may not be "The smartest dog in the world" but more likely, the most brainwashed dog in the world. He then went back to knapping! HH
Pretty neat. Spend enough time with your dog, and you can teach them to do anything.  S.
Pretty cool. Ralphie watched too Joe, and he is in agreement with your dog.
Too bad wives don't listen that well. LOL
wow!  That's awesome!   I wish my fox terrier was somewhat smart.  He's untrainable!
Smarter than a lot of humans
